<br>
You mean recently?  He means during the expansion.  He is right, specially when you compare with other expansions.  Luclin for mages was better just merely as an expansion than Kunark or Velious, theres not much in debating that either.<br>
<br>
Maybe you think what we got wasn't enough?  Well, what can we compare it to?  The best EQ changes?  Say.. what happened with melee's and their AC and damage on weapons?<br>
<br>
Well we didn't recieve a 200% increase (or more) in damage.  We did come a lot closer than you may think though.  In sheer DPS from nukes from focus items and some good nukes with decent ratios and enhanced specialization abilities worked out pretty nice for us.  Now couple that with going from like almost no mana regen to having godly combos with trans rods and in ideal circumstances having mana regen of 100 mana a tick, thats pretty sweet.<br>
<br>
Remember when enchanters were worried not too long ago about Verant giving out flowing thought I items?  Because they were supposed to be the only class that gave a clarity effect to others?  Well now we have stackable flowing thought items going up to KEI levels.  And then of course new spells and abilities that add mana regen too.  <br>
<br>
Mana regen basically was cut into a third of the time now that is was before.<br>
<br>
All that with luclin.<br>
<br>
We can chain nuke now in proper circumstances, and are able to keep it up nearly indefinitly.  Our pets got a crapload of upgrades, even considering the haste cap and FB fiasco.  I mean our epics was upgraded how many times in the last expansion?  Compared to others?  We got higher damage, more hit points, and now a focus item that upgrades it's potential even further?  What other epic has gotten that much of an upgrade?  <br>
<br>
Only gripes we have now mainly come by comparing us to others.  And some of them I can follow.  But just for upgrades alone Luclin, that beta tester is unquestionably right.  I can only hope we do half as well with PoP. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uimmlazen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Immlazen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 72<br> <font color=#333333>(9/26/02 9:49:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm46.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=8.topic&index=44>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Where are the Mage beta testers</span><hr size=1> NO NO NO and More No<br>
